data.description: Charming ranch home in the heart of Spring Hill! Newly remodeled interior! • Stunning upgrade with LVP flooring throughout providing durability for high traffic areas • Freshly Painted • Kitchen Transformation: Luxurious granite, painted white cabinetry, new hardware, attractive under-mount sink with new faucet • New light fixtures • Renovated Bathrooms ~Primary bath with beautiful extra large tiled shower • New Vanities & Mirrors • Tile Flooring • New Roof & Water Heater • New Interior Doors • Great Storage Area behind the attached carport • Ideally situated on a generous .60-acre lot across from Evans Park with ballfields, playgrounds & pavilions • Walk to the elementary school • Close to The Crossings/Shopping, restaurants & Saturn Parkway • With the modern updates & prime location, this home won't be available long. Schedule a showing & make this house your home for the holidays!
